     1	"""Partial-write recovery tests for the admin module (chunk 9e).
     2	
     3	Exercises the failure modes summarized in §I of the chunk-9e plan:
     4	``IllegalTransition`` on terminal reclaim, transport-shaped failures
     5	on read and write paths, the GET-time / POST-time eligibility split,
     6	and the CAS-miss surface on ``GitRepo.delete_ref``. Also covers the
     7	codex-review-driven refinement: ``GitError`` on delete is classified
     8	into CAS-miss vs unexpected git failure, and unexpected failures
     9	propagate to the standard 500 page (not silenced as ``ref-changed``).
